graph TB
    subgraph "KServe Component"
        Controller[kserve-controller-manager<br/>Go Operator]
        Webhook[webhook-server<br/>Go Service]
        Agent[kserve-agent<br/>Go Sidecar]
        Router[kserve-router<br/>Go Service]
        StorageInit[storage-initializer<br/>Python InitContainer]

        Controller -->|validates/mutates| Webhook
        Controller -->|deploys| StorageInit
        Agent -.->|sidecar for| ModelServer
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        InferenceService[InferenceService CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1beta1]
        ServingRuntime[ServingRuntime CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
        InferenceGraph[InferenceGraph CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
        TrainedModel[TrainedModel CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
        ClusterServingRuntime[ClusterServingRuntime CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
    end

    subgraph "Model Servers"
        ModelServer[Model Server Pod<br/>TensorFlow/PyTorch/SKLearn/etc.]
    end

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        Istio[Istio Service Mesh<br/>1.19.x]
        Knative[Knative Serving<br/>0.39.x]
        CertManager[cert-manager]
        Storage[Cloud Storage<br/>S3/GCS/Azure]
    end

    subgraph "Internal ODH/RHOAI"
        Dashboard[ODH Dashboard]
        ModelRegistry[Model Registry]
        ServiceMesh[Service Mesh]
    end

    User[User/CI] -->|creates| InferenceService
    User -->|creates| ServingRuntime
    User -->|creates| InferenceGraph

    InferenceService -->|watched by| Controller
    ServingRuntime -->|watched by| Controller
    InferenceGraph -->|watched by| Controller
    TrainedModel -->|watched by| Controller
    ClusterServingRuntime -->|watched by| Controller

    Controller -->|creates| KnativeService[Knative Service]
    Controller -->|creates| IstioVS[Istio VirtualService]
    Controller -->|creates| ModelServer

    StorageInit -->|downloads models from| Storage

    Controller -->|depends on| Knative
    Controller -->|depends on| Istio
    Controller -->|depends on| CertManager

    Controller -->|integrates with| Dashboard
    Controller -->|integrates with| ModelRegistry
    ModelServer -.->|mTLS via| ServiceMesh

    Router -->|routes to| ModelServer
    InferenceGraph -->|orchestrated by| Router

    Client[External Client] -->|inference request| Istio
    Istio -->|routes to| ModelServer

